quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  101,10,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ bẹ́ẹ̀?"
  101,11,"(Òhun ni) Iná gbígbóná tó ń jó gan-an."
  102,7,"Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú ẹ máa fi ojú rí i ní àrídájú."
  102,8,"Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú ní ọjọ́ yẹn wọ́n máa bi yín léèrè nípa ìgbádùn (ayé yìí)."
  104,1,"Ègbé ni fún gbogbo abúnilójú-ẹni, abúnilẹ́yìn-ẹni,"
  104,2,"ẹni tí ó kó dúkìá jọ, tí ó sì kà á lákàtúnkà (láì ná an fún ẹ̀sìn)."
  104,3,"Ó ń lérò pé dájúdájú dúkìá rẹ̀ yóò mú un ṣe gbére (nílé ayé)."